&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bank Registered Nurse Band 5 AMU &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Pennine Acute Trust&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location: Fairfield Hospital&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Pay rates:Day&lt;strong&gt;: &lt;/strong&gt;£&lt;strong&gt;23.4 – &lt;/strong&gt;Night/Saturday&lt;strong&gt;: £30.42&lt;/strong&gt; Sunday/Bank Holiday:&lt;strong&gt; £37.44&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Do you want to be part of a team that will help motivate and support you? Something that will challenge and reward you at the same time? We are looking for registered nurses to work on MAU at Fairfield hospital   for 3 months.  As a Bank member you will have a choice to work flexibly and get paid the enhanced rates. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;With the support of a dedicated and devoted team you will provide high quality care to patients. You will be involved with the planning, implementing and monitoring of care of acutely ill patients on the ward. You will work collaboratively with the multi-disciplinary team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure safe administration of drugs in accordance with NMC policies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure accurate records are kept in accordance with NMC guidelines&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;In order to apply for a post, you &lt;strong&gt;must&lt;/strong&gt; have a minimum of 6 months experience in a&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In return for your hard work and your professional, caring and reliable service you will have access to the following benefits:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Competitive Pay Rates - &lt;/strong&gt;work this week, get paid next week!&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;First choice of shifts at your Trust&lt;/strong&gt; – Access to shifts before they are available to agency&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Flexible working to suit your lifestyle &lt;/strong&gt;– Take control of when you want to work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Build holiday allowance for every shift you work &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Book and manage your shifts on the go&lt;/strong&gt; – Access shifts anywhere, anytime online or through your smartphone&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Support when you need it – 24/7 365 days – &lt;/strong&gt;Call us anytime on 03332 407 552&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Stakeholder pension scheme &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
